# Protected Files

NEVER modify these files without explicit approval:

- `packages/excalidraw/scene/renderer.ts` — render pipeline
- `packages/excalidraw/data/restore.ts` — file format compat
- `packages/excalidraw/actions/manager.ts` — action system
- `packages/excalidraw/types.ts` — core types

Changes to protected files require:

1. Full understanding of dependencies
2. Running complete test suite
3. Manual QA verification

## How to verify

1. Run `git diff --name-only` — confirm none of the four protected files appear in the diff
2. If a protected file was intentionally changed, run `yarn test:update` — all tests pass with no regressions
3. Run `yarn test:typecheck` — no new TypeScript errors introduced in or downstream of the changed file
4. Perform manual QA: open the app, exercise the affected feature, confirm no visual/functional regressions
